    "**Keep the legacy TDD shape, bolt STRIDE/C4/BDR on** \u2014 rejected: the Form/Armor/Proof shape doesn't map cleanly to the canonical's problem- discovery / use-case / solution-design spine; bolting on produces a hybrid that matches neither (C-01 violated).",
    "**Per-depth templates** \u2014 rejected: reintroduces the doc-shape-on-depth coupling ADR-001 removes."
